A Federal Grand Jury in New York has <COREF ID="10" TYPE="IDENT">indicted</COREF> five more suspects in connection with <COREF ID="7" TYPE="IDENT">the August 1998 bombing of the <COREF ID="11" TYPE="IDENT">United States</COREF> embassies in Nairobi Kenya and Dar - e - salaam Tanzania</COREF> .
<COREF ID="7" TYPE="IDENT">These terrorist attacks</COREF> killed hundreds and wounded thousands of men , women and children .
<COREF ID="10" TYPE="IDENT">The indictments</COREF> raised to 22 the number of those accused in <COREF ID="7" TYPE="IDENT">the bombings</COREF> .
