The latest to be indicted are <COREF ID="2" TYPE="IDENT">Saif Al Adel , Mushan Musa Matwali Atwa , Ahmed Mohammed Hamid Ali , Ahnes Alibi and Abdullah Ahmed Ardullah</COREF> .
<COREF ID="2" TYPE="IDENT">All</COREF> are members of <COREF ID="4" TYPE="IDENT">Al - Qaida , an Islamic terrorist group organized by <COREF ID="8" TYPE="IDENT">Osama Bin Laden</COREF></COREF> .
