<COREF ID="11" TYPE="IDENT">The US</COREF> calls on <COREF ID="1" TYPE="IDENT">the Taliban movement</COREF> to end <COREF ID="9" TYPE="IDENT"><COREF ID="1" TYPE="IDENT">its</COREF> sponsorship of international terrorism</COREF> and hand over the terrorist fugitives <COREF ID="1" TYPE="IDENT">it</COREF> now protects .
